frames.caption: A woman in an elegant, intricately designed wedding gown stands in a luxurious hall, facing a large window with a scenic view. The room is adorned with classical architecture, chandeliers, and floral arrangements, creating a romantic and opulent atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a grand, ornately decorated hall, likely part of a wedding venue. The woman, dressed as a bride, is the focal point, standing gracefully in front of a large window that reveals a picturesque view of the ocean at sunset.

frames.caption: A woman in an elegant gown stands in a luxurious room, facing a grand set of open doors that reveal a serene ocean view under a starry sky. The intricate design of her dress and the ornate decor of the room create a sense of opulence and fantasy.
frames.description: The scene is set in a lavish interior with a focus on a woman in a formal gown. She stands before open doors that lead to a picturesque view of the ocean and a star-filled sky, suggesting a dreamy, almost fairy-tale atmosphere.
